        <td bgColor="black"><textarea cols="70" name="Message" rows="12" wrap="VIRTUAL">[quote]
This is not a rant, so dont treat it as such. Its more of, "I want your opinion type deal." Anyway here is the scenario. *True Story*

I decide to log into EQ to get maybe an hours worth of AA exp. No prob. I login, zone into ME. About 25 people in the zone, ALOT of people near the entrance/exit. Anyway a 60 Chanter has a DC Goranaga as her pet and all she is doing is slowing the mob and sicking her pet on the others. COMPLETELY OWNING mobs. One other Necro in the zone. A 56 Human Female Necro. She is off to the right when you zone from DS. She is grouped with what appears to be a chanter or wizard.

Anyway I setup shop and start my pulling. While Im fear kiting a Spectral wolf, the Female Necro RUNS PAST ME to grab a goranga. Sorta like in between the Goranga Lookout Spawn and the big rocks. She "Apparently" sprung a trap and a Mind Burrower popped.. The MB starts to own her and she turns around and runs right through me. Im looking at the wolf that ol Jibabn is owning then all of a sudden I get hit for all kinds of crazy damage. I stand up turn around and see that this bitch is now sitting behind me looking at me! Ok...np. I run towards her, stand right in her face, wait for the MB to get next to me then cast QVoX. 

MB aggroes her and her Monk pet goes into action. Monk got owned, she damn near died and she FD's. My fear wears off the Wolf so now Jibabn is going toe to toe with the wolfie. I FD, and the MB stands there looking at me. NP. Jibabn finishes off the Wolf, Thx to Splurt, Pyro and Vex. So now, I have a nice Dark Blue target to deal with...no prob. Stand up, run, cast PE, Snare, Then Commence to root/cook while Jibabn rests. Here is the funny part.....

Punk_ass_Necro_546_Partner/shout You Asshole!

Me/ooc Yea right, your punk ass Necro Partner just trained that Mind Burrower on me, I repayed the favor.

Random_PC_03/ooc Haha thats what they get!

Random_PC_097/ooc Wrong class to train.  <---- He must have been an /anon Necro

Anyway the Necro fd/quit and didnt come back for the rest of the time that I was on. My question is... Was the "Kid" wrong, for simply giving back the mob that a PC forgot to bring to his/her camp? Then when they decide they dont want it, he takes it himself?  
[:D]

Azelus Azedon Warlock
Conclave of The Damned
7TH Hammer

